headline: A passenger says a United pilot forcibly removed him from an airplane bathroom. Now he is suing
summary: NEW YORK — An Orthodox Jewish passenger says a United Airlines pilot forcibly removed him from an airplane bathroom while he was experiencing constipation, exposing his genitalia to other flyers...
